> **What this document is.** The submission-artifact counterpart of runtime
> access control: an inventory of every access grant the solution ships or
> enforces — Salesforce permission sets/profiles on the package side, roles and
> scopes on the server side — what each grants, the least-privilege
> justification, and which test user holds which.

